                                         "text":  "### Mathematical Foundations\n\nAfter studying what we understand about the origin of planets, including our own, we can move on to studying them in more detail.\n\nTo achieve this goal, we need to know how to locate ourselves on a planet. Given this scenario, we proceed to study, through mathematics, how to locate ourselves on a planet.",
